ink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-airs-drone-footage-allegedly-showing-surveillance-of-haifa-port-idf-navy-base/00000190-2c03-d2ff-a5d1-7ccf791c0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡攻击拜登：阻止向以色列运送武器是“不可思议的”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-attacks-biden-inconceivable-to-hold-back-arms-shipments-to-israel/00000190-2c13-db38-adff-fcb344ab0000</link><description>当被问及这批武器运输的状况时，美国国务卿表示，这批重载炸弹仍在接受审查，但“其他一切进展正常”；白宫表示：“我们不知道他在说什么”</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 17:36:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-attacks-biden-inconceivable-to-hold-back-arms-shipments-to-israel/00000190-2c13-db38-adff-fcb344ab0000</guid></item><item><title>极右翼以色列向加沙和黎巴嫩扩张的幻想将杀死我们所有人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-18/ty-article/.highlight/israeli-far-rights-fantasies-about-expansion-into-gaza-lebanon-will-kill-us-all/00000190-2c0a-d5f5-a5d6-edea5b220000</link><description>以色列极右翼领导人表示支持将以色列边界扩展到新领土，而他们甚至无法保护目前家园中的平民，他们非常清楚地表明，通过努力寻求政治解决方案来维持以色列人的生存或确保未来是不可行的。在他们的名单上</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 17:01:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-18/ty-article/.highlight/israeli-far-rights-fantasies-about-expansion-into-gaza-lebanon-will-kill-us-all/00000190-2c0a-d5f5-a5d6-edea5b220000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 256 天：本格维尔表示他致力于在加沙定居</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-256-ben-gvir-says-hes-committed-to-settling-in-gaza/00000190-2c40-d39e-a999-7eceae4c0001</link><description>真主党发布了以色列海军基地的航拍镜头，声称该镜头是由未被以色列拦截的无人机拍摄的。 ■ 极右翼部长本-格维尔表示，他致力于在“整个加沙”建设犹太人定居点。以色列此前被他们封锁了数月 ■ 战争进入 256 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 16:53:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-256-ben-gvir-says-hes-committed-to-settling-in-gaza/00000190-2c40-d39e-a999-7eceae4c0001</guid></item><item><title>被排除在外：随着加沙地区危机的加剧，埃尔多安和土耳其被边缘化</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/turkey/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/erdogan-and-turkey-have-been-sidelined-in-the-gaza-based-regional-crisis/00000190-2b6f-dafe-a3d6-3f6f30ee0000</link><description>在土耳其总统抨击以色列和拜登政府的同时，他也试图保护自己国家的利益，例如与以色列盟友阿塞拜疆的经济关系。不管怎样，“第二天”的会谈中没有他的座位</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 15:25:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/turkey/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/erdogan-and-turkey-have-been-sidelined-in-the-gaza-based-regional-crisis/00000190-2b6f-dafe-a3d6-3f6f30ee0000</guid></item><item><title>“黎巴嫩，应许之地的一部分”：以色列救世主右翼瞄准新的定居点领土</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/lebanon-part-of-the-promised-land-israels-messianic-right-wing-targets-new-territory/00000190-2b9d-d340-a1f8-2b9d18220000</link><description>在你对周一举行小型在线会议、着眼于夺回“上帝应许之地”的宗教弥赛亚主义者不屑一顾之前，请记住，他们的约旦河西岸定居点计划在 50 年前似乎同样古怪</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 15:19:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/lebanon-part-of-the-promised-land-israels-messianic-right-wing-targets-new-territory/00000190-2b9d-d340-a1f8-2b9d18220000</guid></item><item><title>报告：新证据显示以色列国防军事先详细了解哈马斯袭击以色列的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/report-new-evidence-reveals-idf-had-detailed-prior-knowledge-of-hamas-plan-to-raid-israel/00000190-2afb-d2de-af9e-6ffbdf700000</link><description>一份前所未见的以色列国防军文件揭示了哈马斯入侵以色列行动计划的令人震惊的新细节；报告概述哈马斯下令劫持 200 至 250 名以色列人作为人质</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 14:53:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/report-new-evidence-reveals-idf-had-detailed-prior-knowledge-of-hamas-plan-to-raid-israel/00000190-2afb-d2de-af9e-6ffbdf700000</guid></item>